Such combination of a branching process with a Brownian motion is also called
 a superprocess (Adler 199,7 Young 2001 -the Hawaii paper), and the addition
 of a global stochastic flow is formalized from a probabilist point of view
 in Skoulakis and Adler (2001).
 
\end_layout

